(C) = map:海岸, x:19, y:29, way:s, symbol:movev, ask:Go to the next map?
(D) = map:タルハ砂漠・北, x:0, y:56
(E) = map:大洞窟Ｂ５, x:8, y:0
(F) = map:火山島１Ｆ, x:22, y:11
(G) = map:タルハ砂漠・南, x:0, y:10

